| Project | Context | Details |
| --------- | --------- | --------- |
| HomericIntelligence/Odysseus | PR #64 rebase onto origin/main, 2026-03-29 | Conflict on docs/architecture.md: 234-line post-migration rewrite vs 3-line incremental update |

